      <acqinfo encodinganalog="541">
         <head>Provenance</head>
         <p>The papers of Richard Dale, British and American naval officer, were
		  deposited in the Library of Congress in 1976 by the Naval History Division. The
		  1801 letter written by Dale to Eaton was purchased by the Library in 1917.</p>
      </acqinfo>
